>没事儿~没事儿~</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返蝗國啦仆街"},{"pid":"2c0707ad0d1905d5b9c21a97aea270956c12fe95","tid":105021,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:22:36.000Z","msg":"完左未"},{"pid":"7166e6da2d4860a73798310c4855d6eb8fe6c055","tid":105021,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三聖村神石妄動惹禍</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高官炸石 兒子猝死</span><br />\n<br />\n當時新界民政署的一位外籍高官認為此乃無稽之談，堅持要將大石炸毀。當再次籌備爆石工程前，該高官的兒子突然命喪於一宗交通意外中。自此，巨石顯靈之說便甚囂塵上。後來，坊眾更請桝當時麒麟崗上「聖廟」（又名「三聖廟」）的執事，並和當局周旋到底。經過一番研究後，該段擴建的青山公路便繞過該巨石而行，而當時的新界民政署署長彭德（Mr.K.M.A.Barnnet）更依麒麟崗上之三聖廟之名，將青山灣易名為「三聖墟」，以作紀念。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/adult/20060502/20060501225420_0000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fadult%2F20060502%2F20060501225420_0000.html&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=6bcc03e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/adult/20060502/20060501225420_0000.html</a>"},{"pid":"9448b43cc66ab89dfe67e4e1af9a938cbd1bd279","tid":105021,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:27:57.000Z","msg":"冇下文？"}]}